%p
  This page will show a link to the appropriate test if it's been long enough since your last attempt (and you're qualified). Otherwise, it'll tell you when this test will be available. 

%p
  - if session[:user][params[:which]+"Ref"]
    You've already passed the #{@names[params[:which].to_sym]} ref test. Congrats!
  - else
    - if params[:which] == "head"
      The HR test isn't available yet as we're not certifying new HR's until the new rulebook comes out. We'll post notices here and on the homepage (amoung other places) when it's ready!
    - elsif @good
      Here's the link to the 
      -# %a{href: "http://www.classmarker.com/online-test/start/?quiz=afd51c7d951f264b&cm_return_test_type=ass&cm_user_id=#{session[:user]['objectId']}"}<
      -#   Assistant
      %a{href: "http://www.classmarker.com/online-test/start/?quiz=#{@tests[params[:which].to_sym]}&cm_return_test_type=#{params[:which].to_sym}&cm_user_id=#{session[:user]['objectId']}"}<
        #{@names[params[:which].to_sym]}
      test!
    - else
      Looks like it hasn't been long enough since your last try! 
      %br
      %br
      Give it another go at 
      %a{href: "http://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?msg=#{@names[params[:which].to_sym]}+Ref+Test+Available&iso=#{@try_unlocked.strftime('%Y%m%dT%H%M')}&p1=784", target: "_blank"}<
        #{@try_unlocked.strftime("%b %e,%l:%M %p")}
      US Eastern Time.
